summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 61E page 150 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 43-48 incl., Block 4, Norris Add., located for 6 lots on the southeast corner of 40th Ave. S.W. and W. Edmunds St., from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) to General Commercial (CG) Zone.
